                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He also</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">to having been before convicted in August</hi>, 1871, <hi rend="italic">
at Somerset**</hi>—<hi rend="italic">
